+ What's This?

This is the Bedbugs Theme, created by [[*user winkwonkboi]] for articles under the [[[department-of-entomology-hub|Department of Entomology]]] setting. On any wiki, simply apply the following code at the top of your page:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:bedbugs-theme]]@@
[[/div]]

//Note: As this is a Black Highlighter based theme, the Black Highlighter theme should also be applied for this theme to work. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here.]]]//

----

